    question: "How do I know that the membership is right for me?",
    answer:
      "If you're an education business owner or tutor who is serious about scaling your impact and income, this is the place for you. Our members include tutors, enrichment center owners, online course creators, and education consultants from all over Singapore and Asia. If you have any questions about the Pro membership, email us at support@edugrow.org.",
  },
