---

<Layout title="Pro Group">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">{groupOffer.title}</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">{groupOffer.description}</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <main class="mt-[140px] sm:mt-8">
      <!-- Pain Points Section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Are You...</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {
            painPoints.map((point) => (
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 flex-shrink-0">
                  <Icon name={point.icon} class="w-full h-full text-blue-500" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">{point.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">{point.description}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Story Section -->
      <section
        class="mb-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white p-8 rounded-lg">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">"I've been there..."</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
            <img
              src="/haris-classroom.png"
              alt="Haris teaching in classroom"
              class="mx-auto mb-6 object-cover"
            />
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              I started my education business journey as a freelance coding &
              tech instructor (or tutor), teaching just a handful of students.
              Like many of you, I was passionate about teaching but struggled
              with the business side of things: hiring, marketing, and
              operations.
            </p>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <Icon
                name="lucide:arrow-right"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
              />
              <p>
                <span class="font-medium">The Early Days:</span> I worked long hours,
                handled everything myself, and barely made enough to justify the
                time investment. I knew there had to be a better way.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <Icon
                name="lucide:arrow-right"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
              />
              <p>
                <span class="font-medium">The Turning Point:</span> Everything changed
                when I started implementing systems and automations. I went from
                the only teacher, teaching 5x per week, to managing a team of teachers
                & tutors, and focusing on scaling my business, which I really enjoy.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <Icon
                name="lucide:arrow-right"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
              />
              <p>
                <span class="font-medium">The Result:</span> Within 12 months, my
                previous education business scaled to 7 figures in revenue, built
                a team of 10+ teachers, and most importantly, impacted hundreds of
                students' lives.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="leading-relaxed mt-6">
              But, I quit my previous education business because I wanted to do
              my own thing. Therefore, I then find something that I could help:
              tuition and education business owners
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Discovery & Growth Stages Section -->
      <section class="mb-12 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">
            "After talking to multiple tutors and educators, I noticed a
            pattern..."
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              There are 3 stages tutors and educators face:
            </p>

            <img
              src="/growth-graph.png"
              alt="Growth stages graph"
              class="w-full my-6"
            />

            <div class="mt-12">
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Foundation Stage</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    You are not consistently getting students and heavily
                    dependent on unreliable referrals. Getting consistent
                    students seems challenging without a clear path forward.
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                    Revenue: $0 - $200,000
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Team Size: Solo</div>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Growth Stage</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    You have consistent student flow but experiencing burnout
                    from handling teaching, admin, and support alone. Scaling
                    beyond one person presents challenges.
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                    Revenue: $200,000 - $500,000
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Team Size: 1-3 people</div>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Expansion Stage</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    You successfully hired team (admin, tutors) but still
                    teaching classes. Feels pressured to remain as the face of
                    business. Growth potential limited by teaching commitments.
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                    Revenue: $500,000 - $1,000,000+
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Team Size: 4+ people</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Solution Section -->
      <section class="mb-12 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">
            The Hard Truth: Ads don't grow your business, systems do
          </h2>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Let me be honest with you: The methods that helped you earn your
            first $100,000 won't help you earn $1 million.

            <br /><br />

            Many people think spending more money on advertisements or trying
            every new marketing trick is the answer. They're wrong. Working
            until you're completely tired won't help either.

            <br /><br />

            As the famous author James Clear says: "You don't achieve your goals
            just by setting them. You achieve what your daily habits allow."

            <br /><br />

            Here's what most people don't tell you about growing an education
            business:

            <br /><br />

            When you're just starting out, you need good systems to turn random
            student recommendations into regular enrollments. You need proper
            marketing and sales methods that bring in new students regularly -
            without you having to work extra hard all the time.

            <br /><br />

            When your business starts growing, you need systems that help you
            work smarter. This means creating standard ways to handle new
            students and teach lessons. Because you can't grow bigger if
            everything depends on you alone.

            <br /><br />

            And when you're ready to expand? You need strong systems that keep
            your teaching quality high even when you're not teaching. This means
            having clear training guides, ways to measure quality, and methods
            to track how well things are going.

            <br /><br />

            The EduGrow PRO group isn't about quick solutions that only work for
            a while. We help you build strong systems that turn your education
            business from a tiring job into something that can grow bigger
            without you working harder.

            <br /><br />

            We've made mistakes before. We've learned important lessons. Now,
            we're here to help you build these important systems without wasting
            years figuring things out on your own.

            <br /><br />

            Because here's the truth: Working IN your business keeps you busy.
            But working ON your business - through systematic, measurable
            improvements - makes you successful.

            <br /><br />

            Are you ready to stop letting your business control your life and
            start controlling it instead?
          </p>
          <button
            class="mt-6 px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
            onclick="document.querySelector('section.py-12.bg-gray-50').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})">
            I'm Ready To Grow to 7 Figures!
          </button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Business Concepts Section -->
      <section class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What You'll Learn</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Here's a preview of what we are gonna cover. Content and schedule may
          vary based on group needs and market changes.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {
            businessConcepts.map((concept) => (
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 flex-shrink-0">
                    <Icon
                      name={concept.icon}
                      class="w-full h-full text-blue-500"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">{concept.title}</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{concept.description}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Weekly Schedule-->
      <section class="mb-12 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Weekly Session Schedule</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="lucide:calendar" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium text-lg">
                  Every Tuesday (Starting March 4th, 2025)
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  10:00 AM - 12:00 PM (Singapore Time)
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="lucide:video" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium text-lg">Online Sessions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Join from anywhere via Zoom</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="lucide:play" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium text-lg">Session Recordings</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  Can't make it? All sessions are recorded and available for
                  replay
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Group Leader Section -->
      <section class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Group Leader</h2>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">{leader.name}</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {
                leader.credentials.map((credential) => (
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <Icon
                      name="lucide:check"
                      class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500"
                    />
                    {credential}
                  </li>
                ))
              }
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/3 aspect-square rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src={leader.image.src}
              alt={leader.image.alt}
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
              onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{leader.image.fallback}';"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <Testimonials />

      <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Choose Your Plan</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <!-- Free Trial -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 order-2 md:order-1">
              <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Free Trial</h3>
              </div>

              <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <Icon
                    name="lucide:check"
                    class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3"
                  />
                  <span>4 Group Coaching Sessions (March 2025):</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3 ml-8">
                  <Icon
                    name="lucide:calendar"
                    class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 mt-1"
                  />
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <div>
                      March 4th, 2025 - How to create your unique selling point
                      as an educator
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      March 11th, 2025 - Create viral social media to market
                      your lessons
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      March 18th, 2025 - How to hire & attract A+ teachers
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      March 25th, 2025 - How to achieve 7 figures education
                      business
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <Icon
                    name="lucide:check"
                    class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3"
                  />
                  <span>Access to Facebook Community</span>
                </li>
              </ul>

              <div class="text-center">
                <a
                  href="https://edu8.org/free-trial-pro-feb-2025"
                  class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-gray-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
                  Join Free Trial
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Free Trial -->

            <!-- Early Adopter Package -->
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 border-2 border-blue-500 relative order-1 md:order-2">
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-500 text-white px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-bl-lg">
                Best Value
              </div>

              <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">
                  {earlyAdopterPackage.title}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">{earlyAdopterPackage.subtitle}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-500 mt-2">
                  <Icon name="lucide:clock" class="w-4 h-4 inline-block mr-1" />
                  Offer ends February 29th, 2024
                </p>
              </div>

              <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                {
                  earlyAdopterPackage.features.map((feature) => (
                    <li
                      class={`flex items-center ${feature.isBonus ? "font-medium text-blue-600" : ""}`}>
                      <Icon
                        name={feature.icon}
                        class={`w-5 h-5 mr-3 ${feature.isBonus ? "text-blue-500" : "text-green-500"}`}
                      />
                      <span>{feature.name}</span>
                      {feature.worth && (
                        <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                          (worth ${feature.worth})
                        </span>
                      )}
                    </li>
                  ))
                }
              </ul>

              <!-- Add delivery note -->
              <div class="text-center mb-6">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <Icon name="lucide:info" class="w-4 h-4 inline-block mr-1" />
                  All guides, templates, systems and workflows will be completed
                  by March 4th, 2025
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg mt-2">
                  <Icon
                    name="lucide:calendar"
                    class="w-4 h-4 inline-block mr-1"
                  />
                  Early Adopter PRO Membership is valid until August 31st, 2025
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Add price comparison -->
              <div class="text-center mb-6 space-y-1">
                <p class="text-gray-400 line-through text-sm">
                  Value Price: ${earlyAdopterPackage.valuePrice}
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 line-through">
                  Regular Price: ${earlyAdopterPackage.regularPrice}
                </p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">
                  Early Bird: ${earlyAdopterPackage.discountedPrice}
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-blue-500">Save $1,800 (75% off)</p>
              </div>

              <div class="text-center">
                <a
                  href="https://edu8.org/early-adopter-feb-2025 "
                  class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                  Join Early Adopters
                </a>

                <p class="text-sm text-red-500 mt-2">
                  <Icon name="lucide:clock" class="w-4 h-4 inline-block mr-1" />
                  Offer ends February 29th, 2024
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Early Adopter Package -->
          </div>

          <!-- Add note about price increase -->
          <div class="text-center mt-8 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <Icon name="lucide:alert-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500" />
              <span
                >Note: This is the only time we're offering the Early Adopter
                Package - 6 Months Pro Group Membership at this price. After
                this, prices will increase permanently.</span
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
